Biyun!

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:35.660
Biyun!

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:50.820
Lin Megumi strapped the bomb onto me

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:51.900
and made me bring it here.

00:03:53.150 --> 00:03:54.660
Sasaki's men discovered it,

00:03:54.680 --> 00:03:55.690
and a fight broke out.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:58.340
The Tonoji family fired the first shot.

00:03:58.870 --> 00:04:01.410
I've told you everything I know.

00:04:05.770 --> 00:04:07.340
We're currently investigating the scene.

00:04:08.360 --> 00:04:09.690
Please wait here

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.660
until we have results.

00:04:15.150 --> 00:04:15.570
Thanks.

00:04:29.920 --> 00:04:30.620
It's all good now.

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:52.250
Joseph Lee's eyes can't see.

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:05.580
By the way,

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:10.250
at the hospital earlier,

00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:13.700
Grand Duke Tonoji suddenly woke up.

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:17.100
Nobody saw that coming.

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:19.580
My cover was blown.

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:21.700
I didn't have the chance to talk to you.

00:05:23.390 --> 00:05:25.020
The only thought in my head was

00:05:25.270 --> 00:05:26.410
that I had to keep you safe.

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:30.250
So maybe I acted a bit rashly.

00:05:31.480 --> 00:05:33.250
Please don't be mad at me.

00:05:34.020 --> 00:05:35.340
In the hospital, you yelled at me

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:36.250
and told me to shut up.

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:38.820
I was a little upset about it.

00:05:42.480 --> 00:05:43.990
But I also told you to shut up earlier.

00:05:45.640 --> 00:05:46.580
So now we're even.

00:06:02.280 --> 00:06:03.410
Also,

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:07.700
as the two of us

00:06:09.160 --> 00:06:10.970
walked from there to the well,

00:06:11.870 --> 00:06:15.260
carrying the bomb together,

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:15.620
I...

00:06:17.960 --> 00:06:20.940
I rambled on with a stream of nonsense.

00:06:21.960 --> 00:06:22.530
Because I...

00:06:23.200 --> 00:06:24.620
I honestly thought at that moment

00:06:25.310 --> 00:06:26.580
I might not make it out alive.

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:28.380
I'm afraid it will be too late
to say it.

00:06:28.400 --> 00:06:29.290
So I...

00:06:30.760 --> 00:06:31.290
You...

00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:34.410
Just pretend you didn't hear any of it.

00:06:34.640 --> 00:06:35.580
But I did hear it.

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:45.260
When I was trapped in the hospital,

00:06:47.520 --> 00:06:48.530
I was pretty scared too.

00:06:50.760 --> 00:06:51.820
After you left,

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:55.140
that room felt so quiet

00:06:57.200 --> 00:06:58.260
like a grave.

00:06:59.870 --> 00:07:01.260
I pricked up my ears,

00:07:02.110 --> 00:07:03.140
listening all the time,

00:07:04.960 --> 00:07:05.940
hoping

00:07:06.990 --> 00:07:09.650
and longing to hear the sound
of the cane again.

00:07:45.310 --> 00:07:45.740
Yeah.

00:07:47.870 --> 00:07:48.940
That exact sound.

00:07:53.200 --> 00:07:55.290
I used to hate hearing it the most.

00:07:57.640 --> 00:07:59.580
Because every time it meant

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:01.940
we had to hide who we were
and face danger.

00:08:08.760 --> 00:08:11.380
But when I heard the sound fade away

00:08:11.400 --> 00:08:13.140
and gradually disappear,

00:08:13.960 --> 00:08:15.820
I was terrified for the first time
in my life.

00:08:22.310 --> 00:08:23.410
I was scared of losing you.

00:08:34.160 --> 00:08:34.620
Ding Yi,

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:41.070
it's not that I don't care.

00:08:44.160 --> 00:08:45.140
I can feel it all.

00:08:51.550 --> 00:08:52.340
Iâ€¦

00:08:56.400 --> 00:08:57.860
Honestly, I've always felt

00:08:58.640 --> 00:09:00.330
I...I'm not worthy of you.

00:09:00.340 --> 00:09:01.500
I am a very timid person.

00:09:01.520 --> 00:09:02.740
Yes, you are.

00:09:05.880 --> 00:09:07.530
But even so,

00:09:09.550 --> 00:09:11.620
you've still done
so many amazing things.

00:09:12.360 --> 00:09:14.620
Hurry and change out my cipher

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:16.340
to prevent any leaks.

00:09:18.670 --> 00:09:19.930
I'm allergic to shrimp,

00:09:20.200 --> 00:09:21.990
but I still asked them
for a plate of shrimp.

00:09:22.040 --> 00:09:22.770
After eating it,

00:09:23.280 --> 00:09:24.650
I indeed broke out in a rash.

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:37.770
I am now the Deputy Director
of the Cryptography Institute.

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:40.980
You won't need to ask anyone else
for help anymore.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:41.980
I'm here with you.

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:44.460
Is it just about saving face?

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:46.740
What do you mean?

00:09:51.640 --> 00:09:52.340
Biyun.

00:09:52.590 --> 00:09:53.530
Biyun...

00:09:53.550 --> 00:09:54.340
Be careful.

00:09:55.520 --> 00:09:56.140
Is that you?

00:09:56.670 --> 00:09:57.380
Yes, it's me.

00:09:57.830 --> 00:09:58.530
I'm here.

00:09:58.880 --> 00:10:00.620
Come on.

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:01.140
Smell me.

00:10:01.700 --> 00:10:02.440
Smell me right now.

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:03.380
Come on.

00:10:03.590 --> 00:10:04.220
Smell.

00:10:04.550 --> 00:10:05.410
Don't worry.

00:10:05.420 --> 00:10:06.620
This is the first official task

00:10:06.640 --> 00:10:08.740
they've given me.

00:10:08.760 --> 00:10:10.770
I won't let them down.

00:10:11.160 --> 00:10:12.650
As for this Sasaki,

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:13.930
I can't let him stay.

00:10:14.280 --> 00:10:15.530
Anyone under Sasaki's wing,

00:10:15.790 --> 00:10:17.410
I won't let a single one go!

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:21.500
I'm not leaving now.

00:10:21.520 --> 00:10:24.020
Please let me finish his mission.

00:10:25.160 --> 00:10:26.650
I want to become Bai Ye.

00:10:27.520 --> 00:10:30.690
Gu, Hongyu, and Bai Ye,

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:32.620
their sacrifice was not in vain.

00:10:33.040 --> 00:10:34.260
I'll be just like them,

00:10:35.040 --> 00:10:36.620
giving my all without holding back,

00:10:37.880 --> 00:10:39.500
and risking everything to save others.

00:10:45.400 --> 00:10:47.260
Every time I see you, I wonder

00:10:50.070 --> 00:10:51.860
how there could be someone so silly.

00:10:56.000 --> 00:10:56.930
You don't know anything.

00:10:58.640 --> 00:10:59.620
You can't do anything.

00:11:03.280 --> 00:11:04.980
You clearly had many chances to leave,

00:11:07.400 --> 00:11:08.810
yet you insisted on staying,

00:11:09.230 --> 00:11:10.670
going down this path to the very end.

00:11:16.160 --> 00:11:17.650
When you left the hospital,

00:11:18.640 --> 00:11:19.860
what you said

00:11:20.520 --> 00:11:22.770
showed you were braver than anyone.

00:11:24.640 --> 00:11:25.740
In the book of fate,

00:11:27.400 --> 00:11:29.380
our names are written side by side.

00:11:33.400 --> 00:11:35.260
At that time, I just wanted to prove

00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:40.260
that until the day I die,
I am a good actor.

00:11:56.400 --> 00:11:57.620
Actually, I have always

00:12:03.070 --> 00:12:04.690
regarded you as my guiding light.

00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:08.290
Like Romeo

00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:14.020
to Juliet,

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:16.460
I only wanted to be by your side.

00:12:23.880 --> 00:12:25.020
But at that time,

00:12:30.280 --> 00:12:31.620
I overestimated love

00:12:34.640 --> 00:12:36.260
and underestimated the revolution.

00:12:42.640 --> 00:12:43.860
Later, I realized

00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:47.620
you're not like Juliet.

00:12:48.760 --> 00:12:49.860
To you, love

00:12:51.400 --> 00:12:53.220
might just be a small flourish in life,

00:12:53.520 --> 00:12:56.930
something extra to make life brighter.

00:12:58.520 --> 00:12:59.620
Even without love,

00:13:01.520 --> 00:13:03.620
you'd still be the bravest fighter.

00:13:07.160 --> 00:13:08.620
That's why I kept pushing myself,

00:13:12.520 --> 00:13:14.140
trying to become someone like you.

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:17.860
You made it happen.

00:13:23.400 --> 00:13:25.860
Although we are not qualified
to talk about love now,

00:13:28.400 --> 00:13:30.380
we all have the right to yearn for it.

00:13:34.590 --> 00:13:35.500
This ring,

00:13:38.000 --> 00:13:39.140
I'll treasure it forever.

00:14:03.520 --> 00:14:05.140
It wasn't given to me by Joseph Lee.

00:14:09.400 --> 00:14:10.740
It was from Ding Yi.

00:14:40.760 --> 00:14:42.220
The shape of this ring

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:45.380
is called a Mobius strip.

00:14:46.880 --> 00:14:48.100
It has only one curved surface

00:14:49.640 --> 00:14:50.860
that loops endlessly.

00:14:52.880 --> 00:14:54.860
No matter which direction they go,

00:14:58.280 --> 00:14:59.860
they are on the same path

00:15:00.600 --> 00:15:02.010
and will inevitably meet in the end.

00:15:41.280 --> 00:15:42.620
In the book of fate,

00:15:46.280 --> 00:15:48.020
our names are written side by side.

00:15:55.400 --> 00:15:55.980
Of course,

00:16:00.280 --> 00:16:01.620
on that very same line,

00:16:05.640 --> 00:16:06.980
stand 400 million Chinese.

00:17:17.040 --> 00:17:17.500
Hello?

00:17:29.310 --> 00:17:32.740
The last stronghold is confirmed too.

00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:39.020
Mr. Liang,

00:17:39.040 --> 00:17:41.530
your intel accuracy...

00:17:45.440 --> 00:17:46.660
You're truly impressive.

00:17:50.150 --> 00:17:51.460
Since this is my show of loyalty,

00:17:51.480 --> 00:17:52.810
I need to do it clean and proper.

00:17:53.550 --> 00:17:55.330
I can't put you in a tough spot.

00:18:00.200 --> 00:18:01.260
I've given you the intel,

00:18:01.280 --> 00:18:02.180
and it's been checked.

00:18:03.310 --> 00:18:04.460
We've been at this all night.

00:18:04.760 --> 00:18:06.740
Now you should tell me
what time the ship departs.

00:18:18.760 --> 00:18:20.530
See Mr. Liang onto the ship.

00:18:20.720 --> 00:18:21.330
Wait.

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:26.850
What's that supposed to mean?

00:18:29.310 --> 00:18:30.180
Mr. Liang,

00:18:31.480 --> 00:18:34.180
don't blame me for playing it this way.

00:18:34.550 --> 00:18:36.220
If you must blame someone,
blame yourself.

00:18:36.480 --> 00:18:38.530
Such a large flour mill,

00:18:38.550 --> 00:18:39.740
with dozens of people,

00:18:39.760 --> 00:18:41.290
just disappeared like that.

00:18:47.790 --> 00:18:50.530
In life, you have to keep a backup plan.

00:19:02.040 --> 00:19:03.810
If I hadn't left myself a way out,

00:19:05.520 --> 00:19:07.530
would you be where you are today?

00:19:12.760 --> 00:19:14.290
Say whatever you want.

00:19:14.550 --> 00:19:15.740
Anyway,

00:19:15.960 --> 00:19:17.910
it is imperative for me

00:19:18.430 --> 00:19:21.930
to eliminate traitors
and save the nation.

00:19:22.700 --> 00:19:23.440
Eliminate traitors?

00:19:25.590 --> 00:19:26.740
If that's how you put it,

00:19:26.760 --> 00:19:28.660
then we really need to have a long talk.

00:19:30.240 --> 00:19:30.980
Chief Cao,

00:19:32.280 --> 00:19:35.540
where's that Late-Ming Heavenly Maiden
Scattering Blossoms?

00:19:42.240 --> 00:19:44.180
After the Shanghai Bureau was bombed,

00:19:45.070 --> 00:19:46.700
this painting turned up

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:49.530
at Vice Chairman Zhou's home
in the Nanjing Puppet Government.

00:19:51.070 --> 00:19:52.490
What a coincidence.

00:19:53.270 --> 00:19:56.460
The person who happened to help you
deliver it to the Zhou residence

00:19:56.480 --> 00:19:57.980
is an old acquaintance of mine.

00:20:00.550 --> 00:20:02.660
I've seen that painting myself.

00:20:03.270 --> 00:20:06.700
The maiden in it
had the most alluring eyes.

00:20:14.170 --> 00:20:15.330
You step outside for a minute.

00:20:25.720 --> 00:20:28.490
That painting had been missing
for a long time.

00:20:30.270 --> 00:20:32.050
You have news about it?

00:20:36.270 --> 00:20:37.250
Chief Cao,

00:20:37.720 --> 00:20:39.730
if I end up dying here today,

00:20:40.270 --> 00:20:40.810
yes,

00:20:41.510 --> 00:20:42.940
I can keep my mouth shut,

00:20:44.510 --> 00:20:46.250
but whether my family

00:20:46.270 --> 00:20:48.180
can keep this secret for you,

00:20:49.240 --> 00:20:50.380
I am not sure.

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:07.900
Sasaki's radio and messages

00:21:08.680 --> 00:21:12.980
are enough to prove
he wanted the Tonoji family dead.

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:16.420
And last night, Lin Megumi's actions

00:21:16.790 --> 00:21:18.800
were also defined by the military

00:21:18.820 --> 00:21:20.790
as undermining the unity
within the Imperial Army.

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:23.530
Now both groups are subject
to the investigation.

00:21:24.480 --> 00:21:27.220
All their operations in China
will be shut down.

00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:32.980
So the New Government's cipher work,

00:21:33.480 --> 00:21:33.900
Mr. Lee,

00:21:35.480 --> 00:21:37.620
can only rely on you now.

00:21:41.750 --> 00:21:42.620
This is

00:21:43.920 --> 00:21:46.250
the confidential radio data
managed by Sasaki.

00:21:48.960 --> 00:21:54.490
Please handle the handover
as soon as possible.

00:21:54.490 --> 00:21:55.400
[Confidential Document]

00:22:11.200 --> 00:22:11.790
How about this?

00:22:13.550 --> 00:22:14.900
This list of strongholds

00:22:15.350 --> 00:22:17.050
can be considered my toll for passage.

00:22:17.720 --> 00:22:19.860
What I have in my hands
is far more than just this.

00:22:22.100 --> 00:22:23.420
Many people in the Wang Government

00:22:23.430 --> 00:22:24.860
have a warehouse in China Hong Kong,

00:22:24.860 --> 00:22:26.770
hiding tons of gold and antiques.

00:22:27.450 --> 00:22:28.990
I'm the only one who knows the location.

00:22:34.920 --> 00:22:37.220
Do you even dare to tell me
the location of the warehouse?

00:22:38.000 --> 00:22:39.810
As long as I can safely
reach Chongqing,

00:22:40.270 --> 00:22:41.490
we'll sign it together,

00:22:41.840 --> 00:22:43.460
and the credit will belong
to both of us.

00:22:52.720 --> 00:22:54.050
Such a big favor,

00:22:54.070 --> 00:22:56.620
just for two ship tickets?

00:22:58.000 --> 00:22:58.460
Of course,

00:22:59.750 --> 00:23:01.050
I also need you

00:23:01.070 --> 00:23:02.900
to give me a Letter of Appointment,

00:23:03.350 --> 00:23:05.490
proving that I'm not a traitor,

00:23:05.510 --> 00:23:09.180
but that you sent me
to infiltrate the Japanese organization.

00:23:22.720 --> 00:23:27.180
Which comrade needs
to blow up Shanghai Bureau

00:23:28.790 --> 00:23:32.090
sacrificing a key liaison point?

00:23:36.510 --> 00:23:38.700
Mr. Liang, I'd love to help you,

00:23:41.510 --> 00:23:43.980
but your story has holes.

00:23:44.960 --> 00:23:46.330
Do you think it has holes,

00:23:47.720 --> 00:23:49.620
or does someone else think so?

00:24:00.400 --> 00:24:02.050
We must give the comrades
an explanation.

00:24:02.070 --> 00:24:04.220
This is Director Dai's decision. I...

00:24:05.310 --> 00:24:06.770
Dare not overstep.

00:24:10.240 --> 00:24:14.090
So what kind of explanation do you need?

00:24:26.480 --> 00:24:26.900
Finally,

00:24:28.440 --> 00:24:30.010
all obstacles have been cleared away.

00:24:38.000 --> 00:24:38.520
What's wrong?

00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:41.050
There's one last thing.

00:24:59.160 --> 00:24:59.730
Who is it?

00:24:59.750 --> 00:25:00.220
It's me.

00:25:03.920 --> 00:25:05.980
Liang, you're finally back.

00:25:06.400 --> 00:25:07.400
Those people at the door

00:25:07.400 --> 00:25:08.440
look so creepy and strange.

00:25:08.450 --> 00:25:09.980
I was so scared alone.

00:25:10.000 --> 00:25:10.700
Close the door.

00:25:14.040 --> 00:25:15.190
Did you get the ship tickets?

00:25:16.070 --> 00:25:18.900
Yes, tomorrow afternoon.

00:25:20.480 --> 00:25:21.570
Thank goodness.

00:25:23.880 --> 00:25:25.040
Hurry up and pack your things.

00:25:29.680 --> 00:25:30.860
Remember to bring my medicine.

00:25:31.920 --> 00:25:32.900
It's all ready.

00:25:34.200 --> 00:25:36.460
Not sure if the doctors
in Chongqing are good.

00:25:37.110 --> 00:25:38.090
But I've prepared anyway.

00:25:38.960 --> 00:25:41.250
If it really doesn't work out,
I'll just sell it

00:25:41.590 --> 00:25:42.730
to help out with the bills.

00:25:45.200 --> 00:25:47.330
If one day we can really move
to China Hong Kong,

00:25:47.680 --> 00:25:48.620
that would be amazing.

00:25:49.200 --> 00:25:50.490
It's pretty close to Shunde.

00:25:50.640 --> 00:25:51.900
My whole family lives there.

00:25:52.000 --> 00:25:53.630
We wouldn't have to worry
about anything.

00:25:55.590 --> 00:25:56.530
People always say

00:25:56.960 --> 00:26:00.380
China Hong Kong is warm all year round.

00:26:00.400 --> 00:26:03.050
Your leg will get much better
over there.

00:26:06.000 --> 00:26:07.980
There's a place called Queen's Road.

00:26:08.000 --> 00:26:10.490
They say all the fancy stuff
is on Queen's Road.

00:26:11.240 --> 00:26:13.380
Rich folks live in Mid-Levels.

00:26:14.160 --> 00:26:15.490
In the Mid-Levels area,

00:26:15.720 --> 00:26:16.980
if you open the window,

00:26:17.000 --> 00:26:19.220
you can see Victoria Harbour
right there.

00:26:21.060 --> 00:26:22.550
Just thinking about it makes me happy.

00:26:36.720 --> 00:26:37.700
When we're settled,

00:26:40.160 --> 00:26:41.700
maybe we could have a kid.

00:26:44.000 --> 00:26:47.250
Before, we kept saying, let's wait.

00:26:48.160 --> 00:26:50.090
We wanted to give our child
a better life.

00:26:51.200 --> 00:26:52.520
I've finally understood something.

00:26:54.270 --> 00:26:56.940
As long as we're both safe and sound,

00:26:57.500 --> 00:26:58.980
that's the best life we could ask for.

00:26:59.920 --> 00:27:00.700
Don't you agree?

00:27:14.750 --> 00:27:15.700
Yin,

00:27:18.070 --> 00:27:19.980
you've been through so much
all these years.

00:27:22.720 --> 00:27:24.250
Good times are just around the corner.

00:27:27.550 --> 00:27:28.220
Very soon.

00:28:11.720 --> 00:28:12.460
Liang,

00:28:15.440 --> 00:28:18.140
we've spent half our lives
scheming against others.

00:28:20.830 --> 00:28:21.770
This time,

00:28:24.240 --> 00:28:26.290
