00:39:54.110 --> 00:39:55.460
Are you out of your mind?

00:39:57.190 --> 00:39:58.420
You were right just now.

00:39:58.440 --> 00:39:59.490
It's just an investigation.

00:39:59.510 --> 00:40:00.460
Not scary at all.

00:40:01.170 --> 00:40:02.340
But things are different now.

00:40:03.030 --> 00:40:04.660
You killed four Japanese
Military Police

00:40:04.680 --> 00:40:06.090
