At the mouth of the alley,

00:40:27.630 --> 00:40:28.940
I've got a car ready for you.

00:40:28.960 --> 00:40:30.210
The key is inside.

00:40:30.400 --> 00:40:32.090
What happened between us in the street

00:40:32.230 --> 00:40:33.570
