of the Gu Family.

00:40:44.440 --> 00:40:45.570
This is your plan, huh?

00:40:47.800 --> 00:40:49.340
You have only 90 seconds left.

00:40:51.000 --> 00:40:52.300
Think it through now.

00:40:52.320 --> 00:40:53.420
Leaving now

00:40:53.630 --> 00:40:55.020
